msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Kui asute Ameerika Ühendriikide väljaspool, soovitame NOWPayments "
"(madalaimad tasud, otse teie rahakotti). Kui asute Ameerika Ühendriikides, "
"on ka Stripe Crypto valik. Saate aktiveerida mitu teenust ja lasta "
"külastajatel valida!"

